    <li><strong><code>tools/schema.md</code> 신설</strong>: <code>knowledge-index.&lt;lang&gt;.json</code>(schemaVersion 2 — docs·related 생성 규칙·stats의 clusters/hubs/topConcepts/bridges/galaxies) · <code>doc-dates.json</code>(ISO8601 KST, 표시=날짜부·정렬=전체·판정=c) · <code>list</code>의 name/path 계약을 명문화.</li>
